data.description: This beautiful home in northwest Minot has been well maintained, nicely updated, and freshly clean - it's perfect for you!  Main floor has all new flooring throughout, kitchen has all new cabinetry, countertops, and appliances.  Down the hall are three bedrooms and a full bath, primary bedroom has an attached half bath too.  From dining room (note the built in cabinetry), a sliding glass door leads to the backyard which is fully fenced and very private.  Patio includes sunshades for comfort in the hot summer months.  Large shed has two compartments with separate entries. Off kitchen is access to the lower level with wood buck stove, large family room, fourth non-egress bedroom, three quarter bath, laundry room, and sizeable utility/storage room.  There will be no lack of space for your holiday décor and other seasonal items!  Attached one-stall garage leads directly into kitchen for your convenience.  Side door provides easy access around fence to a stepped hillside that is already cleaned and maintained - it would be perfect for gardens, flowerbeds, or other hobbies/interests.    Fruit trees in the front and back are perfect for canning, pies, etc.  Street is quickly maintained through winter so access to the property is rarely an issue through our frustrating snow events.  Call an agent today to schedule your private tour, and keep an eye out for upcoming open houses!
